{"title":"消灭钉螺歌","authors":["方志纯"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":10,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"消灭钉螺歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"方志纯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"消灭钉螺齐动手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血吸虫病绝根由。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用火烧来用药杀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钉螺个个命难留。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开挖新沟填旧沟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"裁弯取直水畅流。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钉螺打坑深埋葬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不灭干净誓不休。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沟渠草泥常挖净，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"入窖积肥保丰收。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滨湖草地齐开垦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抢种粮油是良谋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"藏螺水田改旱种，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人畜安全不担忧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粪便经常管理好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"病虫繁殖无自由。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦战三年钉螺灭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地增粮棉人增寿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血吸虫病消灭尽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大壮举传千秋。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}